    <item>
      <title>美国大选前中国放宽限制以吸引全球投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/china-eases-curbs-to-woo-global-investors-ahead-of-us-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国大选前几天，中国正采取进一步措施吸引外资，这引发了人们对唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫对世界第二大经济体造成影响的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/china-eases-curbs-to-woo-global-investors-ahead-of-us-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 16:12:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国大选威胁致地方政府损失数百万美元安全费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/us-election-threats-cost-local-governments-millions-in-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 2020 年以来，针对选举官员的威胁不断增加，地方政府已花费数百万美元来加强对选民、投票站工作人员、选票和设备的保护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/us-election-threats-cost-local-governments-millions-in-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 16:00:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
